Ranger Help for: calm animal
=============================

SYNTAX:      calm <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   9
BASE SP:     45
SKILL TYPE:  defensive

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to use a nature-like demeanor to overcome
an animal's aggression and calm it. A calmed animal stops attacking,
and anything attacking the animal also stops. There is a chance the
animal may become frightened and resume attacking. A Ranger cannot
calm an animal that belongs to their enemy species. The success rate
depends on the Ranger's charisma and skill level.
